{"tid":1367164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［臨急抱佛腳系列］727元朗，200蚊內買齊野餐基本裝備","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:42:26.000Z","uid":100291,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1459cf3cb84ea1127b111adae64e355bff10bc9b","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:27:34.000Z","msg":"由於727太多人表示想去元朗參加宗教活動/睇戲/食飯<br />\n但721元朗發生既事件，人大家人心惶惶<br />\n所以為大家安心唔受傷地進行各種活動，以下有個基本既買裝備地點推薦<br />\n<br />\n大家跟住去就可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>200蚊內買齊基本既保護裝備</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，第一站可以去<strong>深水場電子特賣城</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可購裝備：面罩5蚊，背囊9蚊，冰巾3蚊</span><br />\n關門時間：22:30<br />\n大家可以去到深水埗站<br />\n由D2出口出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8roDBWd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8roDBWd.png&h=8e8ee3fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向住麥當勞方向走一分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwgRcve.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwgRcve.png&h=9055fce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUJDBW6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUJDBW6.png&h=b9de2b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bayW73Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbayW73Y.png&h=a9690ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Z8DBXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Z8DBXk.png&h=b486f4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnbtZaG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnbtZaG.png&h=abf50e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9Qq1o3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9Qq1o3.png&h=51d8ee94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eg9WoCq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEg9WoCq.png&h=e1b5cc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二站，<strong>迪卡儂</strong><br />\n關門時間：22:30<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可購裝備：浮潛鏡 ，太撚多 睇圖</span><br />\n就可以搭我地準時率99%既港鐵去旺角站<br />\n旺角既E1出口 一出就見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMrqgX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMrqgX7.png&h=9303cd8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0oL1p9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0oL1p9.png&h=7a790fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nahg75a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnahg75a.png&h=19794000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNK7vix.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNK7vix.png&h=e1ce0e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2ayqRT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2ayqRT.png&h=e5a3339d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n備註：迪卡隆嘅浮潛鏡可能同某d高級口罩/裝備唔夾，試清楚先<br />\n買完就出番去 去第三站啦<br />\n<br />\n第三站，<strong>先鋒極限裝備</strong><br />\n關門時間：19:30（通常）（19:30後都可以去碰下運氣）<br />\n廣東道918<br />\n一出迪卡儂向山東街行，轉個灣就到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可購裝備：頭盔 30蚊<br />\n（由於老闆自己公司既頭盔已經清曬，新果批係買行家拎番黎所以貴左十蚊，唔好誤會老闆食人血饅頭）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3V6LS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3V6LS2.png&h=296fbe55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tLJ8eMp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtLJ8eMp.png&h=0069e7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsPrLS6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsPrLS6.png&h=d0c3f83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">最後埋數：面罩5蚊+背囊9蚊+冰巾3蚊+頭盔30蚊+迪卡儂既眼罩49蚊+足球護腳pad 69蚊=165蚊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n其他淨低既仲可以買手套同其他裝備Tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後希望大家既活動活心又放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"254eb0c0c29d5fdac4e2baa126c61c6ffb94990e","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再推"},{"pid":"efd0541c623a8b7534348e0d609993bb4e8f3ad1","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbf025e35eff8c1c3a9e009349fc65163c73ead","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f94d664313a2f364c8de1f205c6147c318ee26","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffad24d2e02c96cc4f4383dcf90ff97ebec69d7e","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bf1d2eccc2c8ef4d37c676a2ec74366d1993bf","tid":1367164,"uid":174428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3adb35876bc97d08e4bf26f71df93692cbc9b348","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e82f2418ba69ad71b00faf64f2800218b4c5397","tid":1367164,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:37:04.000Z",